<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Corporate Majdur - India's Employee Community</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: #0f172a;
            color: #e5e7eb;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .back-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #1a2332;
            color: #3b82f6;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            border: 1px solid #3b82f6;
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .header-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            padding: 50px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .header-section h1 {
            font-size: 42px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .header-section p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #dbeafe;
        }

        .content-box {
            background: #1a2332;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }

        .content-box h2 {
            color: #3b82f6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 26px;
        }

        .content-box h3 {
            color: #60a5fa;
            margin-top: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .content-box p {
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #3b82f6;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .quote {
            background: #111827;
            padding: 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: #111827;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #2d3748;
            text-align: center;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            border-color: #3b82f6;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
        }

        .feature-card .emoji {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #e5e7eb;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: #111827;
            padding: 25px 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #2d3748;
        }

        .stat-card h3 {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #3b82f6;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .stat-card p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .vision-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .vision-box h2 {
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .vision-box p {
            color: #dbeafe;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            background: #1a2332;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 40px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #2563eb;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 60px;
            padding: 25px 15px;
            background: #111827;
            border-top: 1px solid #2d3748;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .footer p {
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: #e5e7eb;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: #3b82f6;
        }

        .footer-links span {
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header-section h1 {
                font-size: 32px;
            }

            .content-box {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="back-button">← Back to Home</a>

        <div class="header-section">
            <h1>About Corporate Majdur</h1>
            <p>India's Largest corporate Employee Community</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-box">
            <h2>🎯 Who Are We?</h2>
            <p>
                <span class="highlight">Corporate Majdur</span> is a community-driven platform where Indian employees 
                find solidarity, humor, and real stories. We're the 9-to-5 survivors' club where your boss's "we're like a family" 
                memes are our material, and your appraisal disappointments become our community's heart.
            </p>
            <div class="quote">
                "From salary freezes to micromanagement, from layoff anxiety to promotion dreams... 
                आप अकेले नहीं हो। You are not alone in this cubicle."
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-box">
            <h2>📖 The Story</h2>
            <p>
                It started simple: <strong>real conversations</strong> about corporate life. Employees sharing their frustrations, 
                celebrating small wins, and finding humor in shared pain. What began as a space to vent became a movement.
            </p>
            <p>
                Today, thousands of majdurs (hardworkers) connect here daily. Share their stories. Make friends. Laugh at similar 
                struggles. Because sometimes, the best therapy is knowing someone else got a "See me after the meeting" message too.
            </p>
        </div>

