                    <p>Corporate jokes that hit different</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="emoji">📖</div>
                    <h3>Real Stories</h3>
                    <p>Employee experiences & confessions</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="emoji">🎮</div>
                    <h3>Fun Games</h3>
                    <p>Break timers & escape rooms</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="emoji">👥</div>
                    <h3>Community</h3>
                    <p>Connect with 1000s like you</p>
                </div>                   
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-box">
            <h2>📊 By The Numbers</h2>
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <h3>10K+</h3>
                    <p>Active Members</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <h3>5M+</h3>
                    <p>Monthly Reach</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <h3>100+</h3>
                    <p>Stories Shared</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <h3>24/7</h3>
                    <p>Community Active</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vision-box">
            <h2>🚀 Our Vision</h2>
            <p>
                To build the largest community of corporate employees where <strong>every voice matters</strong>, 
                every story is celebrated, and <strong>no one feels alone</strong> in their corporate journey.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-box">
            <h2>💪 Why Join Us?</h2>
            <p>
                <strong>You've never felt more understood.</strong> Whether you're dealing with:
            </p>
            <div style="margin: 15px 0; color: #9ca3af;">
                ✓ Toxic managers & micromanagement<br>
                ✓ Salary negotiations gone wrong<br>
                ✓ Appraisal disappointments<br>
                ✓ Imposter syndrome<br>
                ✓ Work-life balance struggles<br>
                ✓ Layoff anxiety<br>
                ✓ The dreaded "performance review"
            </div>
            <p>
                ...there's a majdur here who's been through it. And probably has a meme about it too. 😂
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-section">
            <h3 style="color: #e5e7eb; margin-bottom: 10px;">Ready to Join the Survivors Club?</h3>
            <p style="color: #9ca3af; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                Connect with thousands of employees. Share your story. Find your tribe.
            </p>
            <a href="https://instagram.com/corporate.majduur" class="cta-button">Join Our Community →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="content-box" style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <h2>📞 Get In Touch</h2>
            <p>
                Have a story? Want to collaborate? Just want to vent?
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Email:</strong> hello@corporatemajdur.com<br>
                <strong>Instagram:</strong> @majdur24x7<br>
                <strong>Community:</strong> <a href="/" style="color: #3b82f6;">Corporate Majdur Platform</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

